As we see, go ahead and show all

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:33.840
that happened.

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:35.759
This is not normal.

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:41.360
43

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:43.360
major firework

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:45.520
shows were cancelled across

00:01:43.360 --> 00:01:50.079
America, and they had to reschedule or delay.

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:51.600
43 major cities.

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:57.119
That's not normal.

00:01:54.079 --> 00:01:58.798
Philadelphia, Chicago—go

00:01:57.119 --> 00:02:00.640
ahead and show them the

00:01:58.799 --> 00:02:02.560
