00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:36.159
a

00:03:34.239 --> 00:03:38.720
Boston concert and fireworks.

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:41.920
Show them that. So all the Boston fireworks

00:03:38.720 --> 00:03:43.040
got cancelled or

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:44.319
