00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:35.360
the terror in the heartland...

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:37.840
praying over the heartland. So they

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:39.600
didn't have anything, and it was all

00:04:37.840 --> 00:04:41.919
