00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:44.160
Washington D.C. It was major, and so

00:04:41.919 --> 00:04:46.880
it's very interesting to me.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:48.240
Even New York City had stuff going on.

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:52.080
Go ahead.

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:53.520
